- Shin Sol-i.
- Maaf.

29
00:04:01,839 --> 00:04:05,760
<i>Walau apa jua kesilapan saya,
Heon tak pernah memarahi saya.</i>

30
00:04:07,553 --> 00:04:09,305
<i>Cumanya</i>

31
00:04:09,389 --> 00:04:12,725
<i>langkah saya terlalu pendek
untuk menandingi langkah panjangnya</i>

32
00:04:12,809 --> 00:04:14,644
<i>dan sukar untuk saya mengekorinya.</i>

33
00:04:28,449 --> 00:04:30,326
<i>Tapi tak mengapa.</i>

34
00:04:32,703 --> 00:04:35,164
<i>Kerana saya percaya
dia tetap akan tunggu saya.</i>

35
00:04:37,208 --> 00:04:40,378
<i>Seorang lelaki</i>

36
00:04:40,461 --> 00:04:43,756
<i>Amat mencintaimu</i>

37
00:04:44,382 --> 00:04:47,927
<i>Seorang lelaki</i>

38
00:04:48,010 --> 00:04:50,596
<i>Yang gagal melafazkan kata cinta</i>

39
00:04:50,680 --> 00:04:54,517
Jeong Jin-hwan, hari ini saja
dah 121 kali awak nyanyi lagu itu.

40
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:55,893
Betulkah?

41
00:04:55,977 --> 00:04:57,103
Banyak itu saja?

42
00:04:57,186 --> 00:05:00,440
Kalau begitu, saya patut berlatih lagi.
Saya gemar berlatih.

43
00:05:02,650 --> 00:05:06,237
<i>Seorang lelaki</i>

44
00:05:06,320 --> 00:05:08,448
<i>Amat mencintaimu</i>

45
00:05:08,531 --> 00:05:11,492
Ini bukan berlatih, ini pencemaran bunyi.

46
00:05:11,576 --> 00:05:13,286
Awak cuma buat bising.

47
00:05:14,787 --> 00:05:17,206
Sol-i, awak lukakan hati saya.

48
00:05:17,290 --> 00:05:20,710
Suara bakal bintang handalan ini
awak kata pencemaran bunyi?

49
00:05:21,294 --> 00:05:23,045
Nak saya korek telinga awak?

50
00:05:25,506 --> 00:05:27,133
Hantar tugasan matematik.

51
00:05:30,178 --> 00:05:31,179
Nah.

52
00:05:32,430 --> 00:05:33,389
Nah.

53
00:05:34,682 --> 00:05:36,309
Sekejap!

54
00:05:37,810 --> 00:05:39,979
Shin Sol-i, awak meniru lagi?

55
00:05:49,113 --> 00:05:52,200
Soalan kali ini sangat mudah.
Betul tak, Su-jin?

56
00:05:52,283 --> 00:05:53,367
Apa awak merepek ini?

57
00:05:56,621 --> 00:05:59,665
Mi-nyeo, soalan matematik
kali ini senang, bukan?

58
00:05:59,749 --> 00:06:01,542
Saya selesaikan dengan mudah.

59
00:06:01,626 --> 00:06:03,377
- Yakah?
- Ya.

60
00:06:06,255 --> 00:06:09,217
SHIN SOL-I, 35 MARKAH

61
00:06:10,092 --> 00:06:11,761
Awak tahu kenapa dipanggil, bukan?

62
00:06:14,722 --> 00:06:16,849
Markah yang baik memang penting,

63
00:06:17,433 --> 00:06:19,393
tapi kesungguhan juga sama penting.

64
00:06:19,477 --> 00:06:22,230
Cikgu nampak banyak soalan
yang tak berjawab.

65
00:06:25,775 --> 00:06:26,859
Cikgu.

66
00:06:27,693 --> 00:06:29,070
Saya minta maaf.

67
00:06:37,370 --> 00:06:38,829
Jom pergi berkaraoke, nak?

68
00:06:43,751 --> 00:06:46,837
Heon, awak lapang sekarang?

69
00:06:46,921 --> 00:06:47,755
Ada apa?

70
00:06:47,838 --> 00:06:50,967
Tengok ini. Oh Hui-ji.

71
00:06:51,050 --> 00:06:52,093
Awak suka Cha Heon?

72
00:06:52,176 --> 00:06:54,220
Saya boleh baca fikiran awak.

73
00:06:54,303 --> 00:06:55,471
Awak suka dia, bukan?

74
00:06:55,554 --> 00:06:57,556
Awak nak jadi
pasangan pertama dalam kelas?

75
00:06:58,349 --> 00:06:59,267
Betulkah?

76
00:06:59,350 --> 00:07:01,894
Saya tak faham formula matematik tadi.

77
00:07:02,812 --> 00:07:04,021
Boleh tolong terangkan?

78
00:07:04,772 --> 00:07:05,940
Okey.

79
00:07:11,904 --> 00:07:13,281
Hei, Jin-hwan.

80
00:07:13,364 --> 00:07:15,866
Antara saya dan Oh Hui-ji,
muka siapa lebih kecil?

81
00:07:16,576 --> 00:07:19,996
Sudah tentulah Hui-ji.

82
00:07:22,498 --> 00:07:24,083
Soalan awak itu salah.

83
00:07:24,166 --> 00:07:25,668
Tengok saja dah tahu.

84
00:07:25,751 --> 00:07:29,630
Satu, dua, tiga, empat, lima,
enam, tujuh, lapan, sembilan.

85
00:07:29,714 --> 00:07:32,592
Sembilan? Hei, dia lebih
daripada sempurna.

86
00:07:32,675 --> 00:07:34,927
Kamu berdua bagai langit dengan bumi.

87
00:07:43,769 --> 00:07:45,980
Saya buat sendiri.

88
00:07:48,941 --> 00:07:51,027
Awak buat sendiri?

89
00:07:51,110 --> 00:07:53,738
Saya tak pernah jumpa orang seperti awak.

90
00:07:55,156 --> 00:07:58,534
Awak tak perlu begitu terharu
dengan pemberian saya.

91
00:07:59,285 --> 00:08:04,081
Sol-i, awak gadis terbaik
antara semua gadis yang saya kenal.

92
00:08:04,165 --> 00:08:07,793
Saiz muka tak penting buat saya.

93
00:08:49,251 --> 00:08:51,003
<i>Sijo</i> karya Hwang Jin-i.

94
00:08:51,629 --> 00:08:54,924
"Dalam sunyi dingin salju
yang berpanjangan,

95
00:08:55,007 --> 00:08:57,885
berselimutkan kehangatan bayu musim bunga.

96
00:08:57,968 --> 00:09:00,221
Setia menantikan saat

97
00:09:00,304 --> 00:09:02,431
kita bersatu semula."

98
00:09:02,515 --> 00:09:04,350
Puisi Hwang Jin-i ini

99
00:09:04,433 --> 00:09:08,604
menggambarkan cinta serta kerinduan
terhadap insan tersayang.

100
00:09:08,688 --> 00:09:12,358
Dalam istilah moden,
ia boleh dianggap sebagai surat cinta.

101
00:09:12,441 --> 00:09:15,528
Cikgu pernah terima banyak surat cinta.

102
00:09:17,405 --> 00:09:19,657
Cikgu pernah tulis banyak surat cinta.

103
00:09:19,740 --> 00:09:21,409
Paling penting dalam surat cinta

104
00:09:21,492 --> 00:09:23,202
ialah keikhlasan si penulis.

105
00:09:23,285 --> 00:09:25,788
Surat cinta yang ditulis
dengan penuh ikhlas

106
00:09:25,871 --> 00:09:28,165
mampu menyentuh hati si penerimanya.

107
00:09:28,249 --> 00:09:29,834
Ini perkara paling utama.

108
00:09:29,917 --> 00:09:31,711
Baiklah, kita baca sekali lagi.

109
00:09:31,794 --> 00:09:35,464
"Dalam sunyi dingin salju
yang berpanjangan…"

110
00:09:35,548 --> 00:09:36,590
SURAT CINTA DARI HATI!

111
00:09:36,674 --> 00:09:39,176
"…berselimutkan kehangatan
bayu musim bunga.

112
00:09:39,260 --> 00:09:41,929
Setia menantikan saat…"

113
00:09:43,222 --> 00:09:45,516
HAI, HEON. SAYA SHIN SOL-I

114
00:09:48,728 --> 00:09:51,439
- Apa yang awak tulis itu?
- Aduhai.

115
00:09:51,522 --> 00:09:52,606
Jangan menyibuk.

116
00:09:52,690 --> 00:09:54,650
Awak tulis surat cinta?

117
00:09:56,193 --> 00:09:57,528
Awak memang bertuah.

118
00:09:58,696 --> 00:09:59,905
Apa maksud awak?

119
00:09:59,989 --> 00:10:02,533
Jika Hong Sung-dae
pakar formula matematik,

120
00:10:02,616 --> 00:10:05,202
Jeong Jin-hwan pula pakar surat cinta.

121
00:10:06,078 --> 00:10:06,996
Awak?

122
00:10:07,079 --> 00:10:08,873
Hei, sejak sekolah menengah,

123
00:10:08,956 --> 00:10:11,375
- ada seribu surat…
- Awak terima seribu surat cinta?

124
00:10:11,459 --> 00:10:13,335
- Awak?
- Aduhai, dungu betul.

125
00:10:13,419 --> 00:10:14,837
Awak tak kenal Hong Sung-dae?

126
00:10:14,920 --> 00:10:17,506
Penulis buku <i>Seni Matematik</i>. Itu orangnya.

127
00:10:17,590 --> 00:10:21,886
Kalau dia tulis buku,
saya pula pakar tulis surat cinta.

128
00:10:24,054 --> 00:10:25,598
Mengagumkan juga.

129
00:10:26,307 --> 00:10:27,933
Tulis satu pun cukup susah.

130
00:10:29,310 --> 00:10:30,311
Biar saya tengok.

131
00:10:46,619 --> 00:10:48,078
Nak hantar semua surat ini?

132
00:10:48,162 --> 00:10:50,581
Asyik saya saja terima surat.

133
00:10:50,664 --> 00:10:52,625
Saya cuma balas surat mereka.

134
00:10:52,708 --> 00:10:54,210
Ini surat balas.

135
00:10:54,794 --> 00:10:56,921
Awak nak saya ajar awak?

136
00:10:57,588 --> 00:10:58,672
Okey. Aduhai…

137
00:10:58,756 --> 00:11:00,090
- Padam.
- Padam.

138
00:11:02,259 --> 00:11:04,094
Apa awak buat ini?

139
00:11:04,178 --> 00:11:06,263
- Tak sengaja. Maaf.
- Aduh.

140
00:11:06,347 --> 00:11:07,223
Dah.

141
00:11:07,306 --> 00:11:09,391
- Ajarlah saya.
- Okey.

142
00:11:11,769 --> 00:11:13,020
Ayat pertama.

143
00:11:13,687 --> 00:11:15,606
"Hai, Heon." Macam mana?

144
00:11:15,689 --> 00:11:17,107
Oh, Tuhan!

145
00:11:17,191 --> 00:11:19,860
Tak boleh!
Itu terlalu biasa dan membosankan.

146
00:11:19,944 --> 00:11:21,111
Sol-i.

147
00:11:22,613 --> 00:11:25,449
Pertama, permulaan perlu ada impak.

148
00:11:26,158 --> 00:11:28,661
- Okey.
- Beranikan diri.

149
00:11:30,037 --> 00:11:31,872
- Dekati saya.
- "Dekati saya…"

150
00:11:32,456 --> 00:11:34,166
- Awak boleh
- "Awak boleh…"

151
00:11:34,250 --> 00:11:35,501
miliki saya.

152
00:11:36,627 --> 00:11:39,004
Awak tak rasa ayat itu agak melampau?

153
00:11:40,631 --> 00:11:42,550
Ia perlu dinamik.

154
00:11:44,301 --> 00:11:46,679
- Hampiri saya.
- "Hampiri saya."

155
00:11:46,762 --> 00:11:48,931
- Kini awak
- "Kini awak…"

156
00:11:49,723 --> 00:11:51,225
- boleh
- "boleh…"

157
00:11:53,435 --> 00:11:54,728
peluk saya.

158
00:11:56,981 --> 00:11:58,524
Jeong Jin-hwan.

159
00:11:59,608 --> 00:12:00,985
Apa?

160
00:12:01,068 --> 00:12:02,861
Awak memang hebat!

161
00:12:03,571 --> 00:12:04,738
Hebat!

162
00:12:05,990 --> 00:12:08,284
Ada juga hasil saya tulis surat ini.

163
00:12:08,367 --> 00:12:11,912
<i>Cha Heon, sejak dulu lagi saya suka awak</i>

164
00:12:11,996 --> 00:12:14,206
<i>Sempurna tiada cacat cela</i>

165
00:12:14,290 --> 00:12:15,874
<i>Jejaka idaman saya</i>

166
00:12:16,834 --> 00:12:17,918
<i>Terimalah cinta saya</i>

167
00:12:18,002 --> 00:12:20,337
<i>Awak tiada pilihan untuk menolak</i>

168
00:12:20,421 --> 00:12:21,547
<i>Tak boleh, okey</i>

169
00:12:21,630 --> 00:12:23,716
<i>Jika awak tolak</i>

170
00:12:24,383 --> 00:12:26,260
Apa? Kalau dia tolak?

171
00:12:27,011 --> 00:12:28,554
Tak boleh.

172
00:12:31,098 --> 00:12:35,436
<i>Kalau begitu saya akan
patahkan kaki dan belasah awak!</i>

173
00:12:40,149 --> 00:12:42,985
"Belasah"? Kejamnya.

174
00:12:43,569 --> 00:12:44,862
Sekolah ini bahayakah?

175
00:12:45,487 --> 00:12:47,698
Ada orang akan patahkan kaki saya juga?

176
00:12:49,950 --> 00:12:52,661
Betul. Sekolah ini memang menakutkan.

177
00:12:52,745 --> 00:12:53,787
Saya juga menakutkan.

178
00:12:53,871 --> 00:12:56,540
Jadi jangan curi dengar dan pergi saja.

179
00:12:58,250 --> 00:13:00,377
Gaya rap awak memang dahsyat.

180
00:13:01,211 --> 00:13:04,757
Okey. Lepas ini, saya akan layan awak
sebagai kawan saya.

181
00:13:05,507 --> 00:13:08,177
Tapi saya tak curi dengar.

182
00:13:08,886 --> 00:13:10,929
Semua yang lalu di sini boleh dengar.

183
00:13:22,232 --> 00:13:25,361
Yang penting adalah untuk
mencari keseimbangan

184
00:13:25,444 --> 00:13:27,780
antara hubungan dan pelajaran.

185
00:13:27,863 --> 00:13:30,532
<i>Beranikan diri. Dekati saya.</i>

186
00:13:30,616 --> 00:13:32,451
<i>Awak boleh miliki saya.</i>

187
00:13:33,661 --> 00:13:36,705
<i>Jeong Jin-hwan, biar betul!
Biar dia miliki saya?</i>

188
00:13:37,706 --> 00:13:40,000
<i>Kami masih pelajar sekolah.</i>

189
00:13:40,084 --> 00:13:41,251
Okey.

190
00:13:44,254 --> 00:13:47,633
Shin Sol-i, ke depan dan tulis ayat
yang dibaca oleh Ha-young tadi.

191
00:13:49,510 --> 00:13:51,053
Sol-i.

192
00:13:51,136 --> 00:13:52,221
Ya!

193
00:13:52,930 --> 00:13:54,181
- Ke depan.
- Apa?

194
00:13:55,182 --> 00:13:56,642
Yang ini.

195
00:14:10,030 --> 00:14:12,074
KATA PEMERI

196
00:14:12,157 --> 00:14:15,119
ADALAH UNTUK MENCARI

197
00:14:16,662 --> 00:14:19,581
KEIMBA

198
00:14:34,263 --> 00:14:36,849
K-E-S-E-I-M-B-A-N-G-A-N.

199
00:14:39,435 --> 00:14:41,437
- Siapa dia?
- Entah.

200
00:14:41,520 --> 00:14:43,772
- Kacak betullah.
- Saya tahu.

201
00:14:43,856 --> 00:14:44,982
Tentu dia!

202
00:14:45,065 --> 00:14:47,067
Pelajar baru yang sertai kem latihan.

203
00:14:47,151 --> 00:14:49,153
- Biar betul?
- Kacaknya!

204
00:14:51,155 --> 00:14:52,448
Senyap, semua.

205
00:14:53,032 --> 00:14:54,867
Woo Dae-sung, perkenalkan diri.

206
00:15:02,708 --> 00:15:04,376
Hai. Maaf sebab lambat.

207
00:15:05,252 --> 00:15:06,962
Saya atlet renang, Woo Dae-sung.

208
00:15:07,046 --> 00:15:08,130
Salam perkenalan.

209
00:15:16,764 --> 00:15:17,890
Kamu berdua, duduk.

210
00:15:37,034 --> 00:15:38,744
Kawan, kita sekelas.

211
00:15:42,289 --> 00:15:43,665
KESEIMBANGAN

212
00:15:43,749 --> 00:15:45,667
{\an8}Tengok ini. Saya dah bantu awak.

213
00:15:46,919 --> 00:15:48,796
Betul juga.

214
00:15:51,548 --> 00:15:52,925
Kamu berdua saling kenal?

215
00:16:02,935 --> 00:16:03,894
Nah.

216
00:16:04,394 --> 00:16:07,189
Ini daripada Jeong Ji-hwan dari Kelas 1-7.

217
00:16:07,272 --> 00:16:09,483
Okey.

218
00:16:11,026 --> 00:16:12,027
Apa itu?

219
00:16:12,611 --> 00:16:14,238
Kenapa awak ambil?

220
00:16:15,155 --> 00:16:18,534
Biar betul?
Masih ada orang tulis surat begini?

221
00:16:18,617 --> 00:16:19,910
Pulangkan!

222
00:16:21,537 --> 00:16:22,955
"Jeong Ji-hwan, tahun pertama."

223
00:16:23,038 --> 00:16:25,624
"Seorang lelaki amat mencintaimu."

224
00:16:26,667 --> 00:16:28,127
Jangan baca lagi, gelilah.

225
00:16:28,210 --> 00:16:30,212
Siapa penulis surat ini? Panggil dia.

226
00:16:30,295 --> 00:16:31,672
Pulangkan!

227
00:16:31,755 --> 00:16:33,882
Pulangkan!

228
00:16:33,966 --> 00:16:35,509
Sudahlah. Jom.

229
00:16:35,592 --> 00:16:37,636
Kenapa ini? Bacalah lagi.

230
00:16:38,137 --> 00:16:41,265
"Jika awak hulurkan tangan…"

231
00:16:41,849 --> 00:16:43,725
Hei, dengar sini!

232
00:16:43,809 --> 00:16:46,353
Sol-i dan Jin-hwan bergaduh
dengan pelajar Kelas 3.

233
00:16:46,436 --> 00:16:47,980
- Bergaduh?
- Jom tengok!

234
00:16:48,063 --> 00:16:50,566
- Di mana?
- Siapa?

235
00:16:53,235 --> 00:16:54,695
Hei, awak takut?

236
00:16:54,778 --> 00:16:56,697
Awak takutkah?

237
00:16:56,780 --> 00:16:58,824
- Apa yang berlaku?
- Siapa awak?

238
00:16:58,907 --> 00:17:00,576
Saya rakan kelas mereka.

239
00:17:01,869 --> 00:17:03,579
Kenapa baca tanpa kebenaran?

240
00:17:04,163 --> 00:17:05,789
Kenapa? Tak boleh?

241
00:17:05,873 --> 00:17:08,876
Tentulah tak boleh.
Bayangkan awak di tempat dia.

242
00:17:08,959 --> 00:17:10,502
Kalau awak, awak tak marah?

243
00:17:12,087 --> 00:17:13,547
Adakah saya akan marah?

244
00:17:19,011 --> 00:17:22,222
Tunggu. Kenapa ini?

245
00:17:22,306 --> 00:17:23,348
Cakap sajalah.

246
00:17:23,432 --> 00:17:25,559
Lepaskan sebelum saya marah.

247
00:17:28,437 --> 00:17:29,563
- Lepas!
- Hei!

248
00:17:37,905 --> 00:17:39,281
Cikgu datang.

249
00:17:39,948 --> 00:17:42,075
Apa kamu semua buat di sana?

250
00:17:43,493 --> 00:17:44,578
Jom.

251
00:17:44,661 --> 00:17:46,830
Kamu nak ke mana? Mari sini!

252
00:17:48,999 --> 00:17:51,001
Mari sini!

253
00:18:22,950 --> 00:18:26,662
Cikgu suruh awak buat ulang kaji,
tapi apa awak buat?

254
00:18:26,745 --> 00:18:27,829
Bangun!

255
00:18:30,082 --> 00:18:31,333
Apa ini?

256
00:18:31,416 --> 00:18:33,126
Aduhai.

257
00:18:37,714 --> 00:18:39,424
"Maafkan saya.

258
00:18:39,508 --> 00:18:43,887
Kerana insan seperti saya
teramat mencintai awak."

259
00:18:43,971 --> 00:18:47,683
Aduhai, mengarut betul.

260
00:18:48,684 --> 00:18:50,185
Cikgu.

261
00:18:50,769 --> 00:18:53,188
Kenapa awak tak pergi berlatih?

262
00:18:54,314 --> 00:18:55,440
Pergi cepat.

263
00:18:57,192 --> 00:18:58,860
"Saya menunggu.

264
00:18:58,944 --> 00:19:01,071
Saya serba kekurangan

265
00:19:01,154 --> 00:19:04,408
dan walaupun tak layak,
saya dambakan awak.

266
00:19:05,575 --> 00:19:07,452
Walau saya…"

267
00:19:13,542 --> 00:19:14,626
Ada apa?

268
00:19:14,710 --> 00:19:17,713
Dalam peraturan sekolah,
tiada larangan menulis surat cinta.

269
00:19:20,340 --> 00:19:21,967
Ini pelanggaran hak asasi.

270
00:19:22,050 --> 00:19:23,385
Apa awak merepek ini?

271
00:19:23,468 --> 00:19:26,138
Menurut Akta 2 Fasal 4
Ordinan Hak Asasi Pelajar,

272
00:19:26,221 --> 00:19:28,515
hak asasi pelajar bermaksud
martabat, nilai…

273
00:19:28,598 --> 00:19:30,142
Hei! Senyap!

274
00:19:30,684 --> 00:19:33,895
Awak fikir cikgu akan beri muka
kepada pelajar terbaik?

275
00:19:33,979 --> 00:19:35,272
Budak bertuah.

276
00:19:36,106 --> 00:19:37,232
Berdiri di belakang!

277
00:19:39,276 --> 00:19:40,527
Awak melawan?

278
00:19:45,032 --> 00:19:46,158
Budak tak guna.

279
00:19:50,954 --> 00:19:52,164
Menjawab pula.

280
00:19:52,748 --> 00:19:54,583
Di mana saya berhenti?

281
00:19:55,667 --> 00:19:58,795
"Saya boleh mengembara ke seluruh dunia.

282
00:19:58,879 --> 00:20:02,215
Saya boleh terus mencari.

283
00:20:02,299 --> 00:20:05,510
Namun saya sedar awak satu-satunya

284
00:20:05,594 --> 00:20:08,138
yang ingin saya miliki.

285
00:20:08,221 --> 00:20:10,557
- Cintailah…"
<i>- Cintailah saya</i>

286
00:20:11,391 --> 00:20:14,186
<i>Jangan biar saya menangis</i>

287
00:20:15,187 --> 00:20:17,272
<i>Satu ungkapan</i>

288
00:20:17,356 --> 00:20:21,985
<i>Yang kerap dilafaz bak nafas</i>

289
00:20:22,069 --> 00:20:25,197
<i>- Diri terasa kecil
- Diri terasa kecil</i>

290
00:20:25,280 --> 00:20:28,784
<i>- Dan sentiasa berselindung
- Dan sentiasa berselindung</i>

291
00:20:28,867 --> 00:20:34,414
<i>- Saya seorang pengecut
- Saya seorang pengecut</i>

292
00:20:34,998 --> 00:20:36,291
Kamu semua, senyap!

293
00:20:36,375 --> 00:20:37,918
<i>Cinta</i>

294
00:20:38,001 --> 00:20:40,837
<i>- Yang makin membuak
- Yang makin membuak</i>

295
00:20:41,421 --> 00:20:42,464
Apa ini?

296
00:20:42,547 --> 00:20:44,341
<i>- Ingin juga</i>
- Senyap!

297
00:20:44,424 --> 00:20:49,096
<i>- Saya luahkan
- Saya luahkan</i>

298
00:20:49,179 --> 00:20:50,847
<i>- Seperti anak yang sesat</i>
- Sini!

299
00:20:50,931 --> 00:20:53,392
Kamu dah hilang akal? Budak bertuah!

300
00:20:53,475 --> 00:20:54,935
Kamu semua…

301
00:20:55,018 --> 00:20:56,812
Apa ini?

302
00:20:56,895 --> 00:20:58,355
Hei, mari sini!

303
00:21:02,442 --> 00:21:05,320
SURAT MINTA MAAF

304
00:21:09,116 --> 00:21:10,784
Jumpa lagi, semua.

305
00:21:20,627 --> 00:21:24,256
"Saya percaya penyalahgunaan kuasa guru
untuk mengabaikan hak asasi pelajar

306
00:21:24,339 --> 00:21:28,009
dan mendedahkan isi kandungan
surat yang bersifat peribadi

307
00:21:28,510 --> 00:21:30,262
adalah tindakan yang tidak adil."

308
00:21:32,848 --> 00:21:34,599
Awak tak boleh tulis begini.

309
00:21:34,683 --> 00:21:36,643
Ini tak berbunyi seperti awak minta maaf.

310
00:21:37,144 --> 00:21:39,980
Ini kepakaran saya. Biar saya bantu awak.

311
00:21:45,485 --> 00:21:47,404
Ha-young…

312
00:21:47,904 --> 00:21:50,699
Siang tadi awak sangat bergaya.

313
00:21:51,950 --> 00:21:53,702
Kenapa awak berdiam diri?

314
00:21:53,785 --> 00:21:55,495
Awak patut belasah dia.

315
00:21:56,288 --> 00:21:57,372
Betul.

316
00:21:57,456 --> 00:22:00,876
Hei, pakar surat cinta, Jeong Jin-hwan.

317
00:22:01,460 --> 00:22:03,086
Semua itu lirik lagu.

318
00:22:04,379 --> 00:22:06,673
Maaf, tapi saya akan belanja karaoke.

319
00:22:07,340 --> 00:22:08,717
- Setuju?
- Tak nak.

320
00:22:08,800 --> 00:22:10,135
- Saya sibuk.
- Saya juga.

321
00:22:13,930 --> 00:22:15,974
Saya juga. Saya ikut kawan saya.

322
00:22:16,475 --> 00:22:20,061
SENYAP

323
00:22:24,316 --> 00:22:28,069
Aduhai, tentu Heon dah pergi ke sekolah.

324
00:22:40,665 --> 00:22:42,250
- Awak tunggu apa?
- Apa?

325
00:22:42,334 --> 00:22:44,085
Tak ada apa. Jom.

326
00:22:52,135 --> 00:22:53,261
Kenapa awak tersengih?

327
00:22:53,345 --> 00:22:57,182
Saya sangat gembira
ke sekolah bersama awak.

328
00:23:13,615 --> 00:23:16,284
<i>Walaupun dia tak terima surat cinta saya,</i>

329
00:23:16,868 --> 00:23:19,496
<i>tapi seolah-olah dia faham perasaan saya.</i>

330
00:23:20,163 --> 00:23:25,627
{\an8}AKAN BERSAMBUNG

331
00:23:59,869 --> 00:24:03,707
Heon, makan ini.

332
00:24:33,320 --> 00:24:36,114
<i>Apa perkara yang boleh ceriakan awak?</i>

333
00:24:36,698 --> 00:24:39,326
- Boleh saya ikut sama?
<i>- Jangan ikut saya.</i>

334
00:24:39,409 --> 00:24:42,412
<i>Bukankah dah memadai
jika awak ada di sisinya?</i>

335
00:24:42,495 --> 00:24:43,747
<i>- Maaf.
- Jom ke karaoke!</i>

336
00:24:43,830 --> 00:24:45,665
<i>Awak yang paling hebat!</i>

337
00:24:46,249 --> 00:24:47,542
Dia cuma perlukan awak.

338
00:24:47,625 --> 00:24:49,377
<i>Jangan ganggu saya. Pergi.</i>

339
00:24:49,461 --> 00:24:51,004
<i>Susahkah untuk minta bantuan?</i>

340
00:24:58,219 --> 00:25:00,472
Terjemahan sari kata oleh Hazizah Ali

